Algorithms

Class Convertors

  • java.lang.Object
    • Algorithms.Convertors

  • public class Convertors
extends java.lang.Object
    this class calculates converts from pixels to gps and gps to pixels. the constructors must recive the top right GPS coordinate and the bottom left GPS coordinate in order to calculate the rations.
